    <!-- Full labels and help copy on tablet (smallest width ≥ 600dp). Default values/ strings stay compact for phones. -->
    <string name="bpm_auto_follow_help">Check Follow AUTO BPM on the top panel. Requires Start Monitoring. Mic when idle; PLAY/SHOT uses the sampler. If the clip came from a **bar-quantized** source (preset bar, quantized REC, library clip with bar count), tempo is **exact** from loop length (4/4) × Sample Pitch—no guessing. Otherwise onset detection is used. BPM LOCK LED still reflects confidence for mic/unquantized sampler.</string>
